Use the standard library
This is how to anti_shuffle of s:
   Remember that n is s's length
   Remember that half is quotient of n and 2
   Remember that result is []

   Remember that i is 0
   Do this half times:
      Add result to item (sum of i and 1) in s
      Add result to item i in s
      Remember that i is sum of i and 2
   End do

   When remainder of n and 2 is 1, then:
      Add result to item (diff of n and 1) in s
   End when

   The answer is result
Now you know